name: Revenge of the Fish
description:
Revenge of the Fish

Survival of the fittest!

The sea creatures have had enough and are starting to fight back. Over the course of the game, they will evolve and adapt to the ever new challengers. How long will you be able to keep the ocean clean from pollution and garbage?
